{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 2431718, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我也是这样认为的", "timestamp": 1630735722, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2431723, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不过实在非要这样操作，咱们也没办法。人家可以说，二次分配的名额本来就是剩下的，想怎么分由人家说了算 不遵守第一次名额的分配规则", "timestamp": 1630735810, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2431765, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2431723, "tag": null, "text": "Re Alice: 但是每个院系的规则都是按照综合排名排，按你说的这么操作势必会出现排名高的没名额而排名低的有名额，这样其实就可以向教育部举报了", "timestamp": 1630736138, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2431803, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "所以现在是连预推免还没有开始是吗？清华那个系统的志愿是预推免？", "timestamp": 1630736473, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2431835, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2431765, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 醒醒，教育部可没说名额就按成绩给", "timestamp": 1630736674, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2431857, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2431835, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 但是现在已经出来的第一批名额分配就是按照各个院系的所谓“综合成绩”排的，这部分同学应该是铁拿名额了，去哪就是各凭本事了", "timestamp": 1630736842, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2431908, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2431857, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: no 这一批之后没offer的名额会被顺延", "timestamp": 1630737086, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2431985, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2431908, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 啊？那这一批有没有offer是等所有学校预推免都结束吗，很多外校的预推免都没开始呢。万一人拿名额要外推怎么办", "timestamp": 1630737557, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2432006, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2431835, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 《关于做好2021年推荐优秀应届本科毕业生免试攻读研究生工作的通知》(教学司函〔2020〕38号)\n（二）突出考查学生的一贯学业表现。注重并加强学生在学期间的过程性评价，将本科阶段学业综合成绩作为推免工作最基础的遴选指标，不得专门组织遴选推免生的考试（包括笔试、面试等）。", "timestamp": 1630737713, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2432027, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2432006, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 清华分配第一批资格就是按照这个综合成绩的啊（不过听说无系是面试确定资格），后面的面试是预推免了吧", "timestamp": 1630737855, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2432030, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2432006, "tag": null, "text": "Re Dave: 确定名额的时候不准考试，没说录取的环节不让考试😂", "timestamp": 1630737868, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2432042, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2431908, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 来源？", "timestamp": 1630737954, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2432043, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "在填教育部系统当天，会有好多放鸽子的，因此很多地方都会多出offer，基本上只要有资格，肯定能找到接收的地方，甚至可以捡漏", "timestamp": 1630737962, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2432047, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2432030, "tag": null, "text": "Re Eve: Carol说的就是确定名额呀", "timestamp": 1630738002, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2432116, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2432043, "tag": null, "text": "Re Grace: 真的吗 所以那时候名额还可以捡漏？", "timestamp": 1630738748, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2432260, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2431908, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 不存在的，学校没理由剥夺学生填报国家系统的权利", "timestamp": 1630740517, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2432514, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2432043, "tag": null, "text": "所以现在是在哪一步呢？没有听说现在需要到学信网上填写任何资料？", "timestamp": 1630742813, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2432523, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2432514, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 还在预推免", "timestamp": 1630742886, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2432560, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2432523, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 那逻辑上是我们拿到推荐名额->参加复试->国家官方系统填材料->然后就ok了？", "timestamp": 1630743119, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2432604, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2432560, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 嗯嗯是的", "timestamp": 1630743442, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2432639, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2432604, "tag": null, "text": "Re 洞主: 嗯嗯谢谢加油～", "timestamp": 1630743677, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2432641, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Grace", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2432116, "tag": null, "text": "Re Carol: 但是会很惊险，一般学校/研究所都会要求学生在开放填报的当天连夜填报，然后凌晨就把学生锁定，我一个同学就抻住了，没有填，白天下午自动化所就多出几个别人鸽掉的offer，同学打车过去见了个面现场填了自动化所", "timestamp": 1630743692, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2432941, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2432027, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 无系第一批资格也不是按照面试啊（今年", "timestamp": 1630745791, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 2434584, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 463301, "reply_to": 2432027, "tag": null, "text": "Re Bob: 无系也是根据综合成绩确定推荐资格，外推/交叉的学生不需要面试", "timestamp": 1630759693, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {"h": 1507, "w": 856}, "likenum": 88, "pid": 463301, "reply": 24, "tag": null, "text": "根据下图，只要有推免名额，就可以填报教育部系统。即使在夏令营和预推免没有得到任何offer，也存在被录取的可能性。所以根据offer来分配名额肯定不合适，A比B排名靠前，但是B有offer而A没有，可这不代表A就不会有。除非A本人同意放弃保研，把A的名额让给B肯定是有违程序正义的", "timestamp": 1630735656, "type": "image", "updated_at": 1630759696, "url": "nb/nb6ywj5kmw2gwoms5buu3ccszb4hcf2h.jpeg", "vote": {}}}